B -> 1 { B.val = 1 }
L -> B { L.val = B.val; L.len = 1 }

S -> L { S.val = L.val }
S -> L1 . L2 { S.val = L1.val + L2.val / 2^(L2.len) }
Verification: 101.101 -> L1.val=5, L1.len=3, L2.val=5, L2.len=3
S.val = 5 + 5/2^3 = 5 + 5/8 = 5 + 0.625 = 5.625 ✓

